OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start, before the clouds
OL,6,Fbubble up to give another day of sunny
OL,7,Fspells and showers. The showers will
OL,8,Fbe heavy, with the risk of hail and
OL,9,Fthunder. A breezy day, locally gusty
OL,10,Fnear heavier showers. Feeling cool.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny daytime showers slowly
OL,13,Feasing to leave a largely dry night,
OL,14,Fwith clear spells developing for many.
OL,15,FTurning locally chilly, especially in
OL,16,Fsome prone rural spots. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
