OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloud and outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fwill spread eastwards across all parts
OL,7,Fduring the day. Rain will be locally
OL,8,Fheavy, especially on western hills.
OL,9,FWindy, locally gusty on hills. Feeling
OL,10,Fhumid.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVariable
OL,13,Fcloud with some outbreaks of rain or
OL,14,Fshowers Friday, mainly on western
OL,15,Fhills. Brighter in the east. Breezy.
OL,16,FDry with sunny spells on Saturday and
OL,17,FSunday. Temperatures nearer average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
